Subject: Payment for your contribution to {{escapeForSubject collective.name}} refunded by the Fiscal Host

{{> header}}

{{> toplogo}}

{{#if fromCollective.name}}
<p>Hi {{fromCollective.name}},</p>
{{else}}
<p>Hello,</p>
{{/if}}

<p>A payment for your contribution to {{>linkCollective collective=collective}} has been refunded by {{host.name}}, the Fiscal Host of {{collective.name}}.</p>

{{#if hostAction.cancel}}
<p>Your recurring contribution has also been cancelled. No further charges will be made for this contribution.</p>
{{/if}}

{{#if hostAction.removeAsContributor}}
<p>You have also been removed as a contributor and will no longer appear on the Collective's public profile.</p>
{{/if}}

{{#if messageForContributors}}
<p>Here is the message from the Fiscal Host:</p>
<blockquote style="color: #6a737d;font-size: 14px; text-align: left;padding: 0.5em 0.75em;margin: 1em 0;border-left: 3px solid #e4e4e4;white-space: pre-line;">{{{messageForContributors}}}</blockquote>
{{/if}}

<p>The refund should appear on your statement within a few business days, depending on your payment provider.</p>

<p>If you have questions, contact <a href="mailto:support@opencollective.com">support@opencollective.com</a>.</p>

<p>
  Warmly,<br>
  – {{host.name}}
</p>

{{> footer}}
